<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٨-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ أَبِي هَارُونَ أَنَّ إِسْحَاقَ حَدَّثَهُمْ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٣٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَأَلْتُ أَحْمَدَ عَنِ الرَّجُلِ يَأْخُذُ مِنْ عَارِضَيْهِ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> يَأْخُذُ مِنَ اللِّحْيَةِ مَا فَضُلَ عَنِ الْقَبْضَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَحَدِيثِ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">((أَحِفُّوا الشَّوَارِبَ وَأَعْفُوا اللِّحَى)</span>) ؟<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> يَأْخُذُ مِنْ طُولِهَا وَمِنْ تَحْتِ حَلْقِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَرَأَيْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ يُأْخُذُ مِنْ طُولِهَا وَمِنْ تَحِتِ حَلْقِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>